                    <img class="img-fluid kirkus-prize" src="https://d1fd687oe6a92y.cloudfront.net/img/kir_images/icons/kirkus-prize.png" alt="kirkus prize">
                </li>
                <li class="list-inline-item align-middle feature-content">
                    <p class="title">The Kirkus Prize</p>
                    <p>The Kirkus Prize is among the richest literary awards in America, awarding $50,000 in three categories annually.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


